<L>__{interior large courtroom day}
<A>__{joe (william) is lead into the courtroom by guards. takes his place at the defense table which includes elliot and two young attorneys. the prosecution table, which includes richard stein and helen is going over last minute minutia. people are taking seats in the gallery. but another attorney joins the defense table. it's arthur baylor. and richard stein double takes when he sees him.}
<B>__{at the prosecution table}
<C>__{richard stein}
